headline: Williams-Sonoma (NYSE:WSM) Declines 11% Despite New Pottery Barn Teen MLS Collection
summary: Williams-Sonoma (NYSE:WSM) saw its shares decline 11.1% over the past week despite recent efforts to enhance its product lines through strategic collaborations. The company announced two significant product-related initiatives: a new collection in collaboration with Major League Soccer via Pottery Barn Teen, and an expansion of its Modern Baby collection through Pottery Barn Kids, both emphasizing sustainability and customer engagement.
